publish.longDesc=This\ game\ was\ created\ as\ part\ of\ a\ Computer\ Science\ assignment.\ I\ developed\ it\ with\ the\ help\ of\ AI\ tools\ such\ as\ Gemini,\ ChatGPT,\ DeepSeek,\ and\ Antigravity.\n\nThe\ character\ assets\ were\ sourced\ from\ platforms\ like\ itch.io\ and\ GameArt2D.\ Some\ backgrounds\ and\ other\ assets\ were\ generated\ using\ Nano\ Banana\ (Gemini)\ and\ sourced\ from\ Pinterest.
publish.shortDesc=Ethereal\ Gate\ is\ a\ pixel\ style\ action\ game\ where\ you\ fight\ through\ waves\ of\ monsters\ and\ powerful\ bosses\ across\ multiple\ stages.\ Sharpen\ your\ skills,\ survive\ the\ battles,\ and\ uncover\ what\ lies\ beyond\ the\ mysterious\ gate.
publish.tags=game\ mouse\ pixel\ action\ adventure\ fantasy\ with-source
publish.title=Ethereal\ Gate
